Mat 13:15 <mark class='poetry'></mark> <strong><mark class='verb'>Ἐπαχύνθη</mark></strong> <strong>γὰρ</strong> <strong>ἡ</strong> <strong>καρδία</strong> <strong>τοῦ</strong> <strong>λαοῦ</strong> <strong>τούτου <mark class='punctuation'>,</mark> </strong> <mark class='poetry'></mark> <strong>Καὶ</strong> <strong>τοῖς</strong> <strong>ὠσὶν</strong> <strong>βαρέως</strong> <strong><mark class='verb'>ἤκουσαν</mark></strong> <mark class='poetry'></mark> <strong>Καὶ</strong> <strong>τοὺς</strong> <strong>ὀφθαλμοὺς</strong> <strong>αὐτῶν</strong> <strong><mark class='verb'>ἐκάμμυσαν</mark> <mark class='punctuation'>,</mark> </strong> <mark class='poetry'></mark> <strong>Μήποτε</strong> <strong><mark class='verb'>ἴδωσιν</mark></strong> <strong>τοῖς</strong> <strong>ὀφθαλμοῖς</strong> <mark class='poetry'></mark> <strong>Καὶ</strong> <strong>τοῖς</strong> <strong>ὠσὶν</strong> <strong><mark class='verb'>ἀκούσωσιν</mark></strong> <mark class='poetry'></mark> <strong>Καὶ</strong> <strong>τῇ</strong> <strong>καρδίᾳ</strong> <strong><mark class='verb'>συνῶσιν</mark></strong> <mark class='poetry'></mark> <strong>Καὶ</strong> <strong><mark class='verb'>ἐπιστρέψωσιν</mark></strong> <strong>Καὶ</strong> <strong><mark class='verb'>ἰάσομαι</mark></strong> <strong>αὐτούς <mark class='punctuation'>.</mark>  </strong>【因為這百姓油蒙了心，耳朵發沉，眼睛閉著，恐怕眼睛看見，耳朵聽見，心裡明白，回轉過來，我就醫治他們。】<mark class='paragraph'></mark>
