Mar 4:25 ὃς γὰρ <mark class='verb'>ἔχει</mark> <mark class='punctuation'>,</mark> <mark class='verb'>δοθήσεται</mark> αὐτῷ <mark class='punctuation'>·</mark> καὶ ὃς οὐκ <mark class='verb'>ἔχει</mark> <mark class='punctuation'>,</mark> καὶ ὃ <mark class='verb'>ἔχει</mark> <mark class='verb'>ἀρθήσεται</mark> ἀπ᾽ αὐτοῦ <mark class='punctuation'>.</mark>【因為有的，還要給他；沒有的，連他所有的也要奪去。】<mark class='paragraph'></mark>
