Luk 20:43 <mark class='poetry'></mark> <strong>Ἕως</strong> <strong>ἂν</strong> <strong><mark class='verb'>θῶ</mark></strong> <strong>τοὺς</strong> <strong>ἐχθρούς</strong> <strong>σου</strong> <mark class='poetry'></mark> <strong>Ὑποπόδιον</strong> <strong>τῶν</strong> <strong>ποδῶν</strong> <strong>σου <mark class='punctuation'>.</mark>  </strong>【等我使你仇敵作你的腳凳。】<mark class='paragraph'></mark>
