Act 7:50 <mark class='poetry'></mark> <strong>οὐχὶ</strong> <strong>ἡ</strong> <strong>χείρ</strong> <strong>μου</strong> <strong><mark class='verb'>ἐποίησεν</mark></strong> <strong>ταῦτα</strong> <strong>πάντα <mark class='punctuation'>;</mark>  </strong>【這一切不都是我手所造的麼？】<mark class='paragraph'></mark>
