1Th 5:24 πιστὸς ὁ <mark class='ptc'>καλῶν</mark> ὑμᾶς <mark class='punctuation'>,</mark> ὃς καὶ <mark class='verb'>ποιήσει</mark> <mark class='punctuation'>.</mark>【那召你們的本是信實的，他必成就這事。】<mark class='paragraph'></mark>
