Heb 9:20 <mark class='ptc'>λέγων</mark> <mark class='punctuation'>·</mark> <mark class='poetry'></mark> Τοῦτο <strong>τὸ</strong> <strong>αἷμα</strong> <strong>τῆς</strong> <strong>διαθήκης</strong> <strong>ἧς</strong> <strong><mark class='verb'>ἐνετείλατο</mark></strong> <strong>πρὸς</strong> <strong>ὑμᾶς</strong> <strong>ὁ</strong> <strong>Θεός <mark class='punctuation'>.</mark>  </strong>【這血就是神與你們立約的憑據。】<mark class='paragraph'></mark>
